    eq: "\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} b_n^2 = \\sum_{k=0}^{\\infty}\\left(\\frac{4}{(2k+1)\\pi}\\right)^2 = \\frac{16}{\\pi^2}\\sum_{k=0}^{\\infty}\\frac{1}{(2k+1)^2}"
