        f(z\u2080) = ${fre.toFixed(4)} + ${fim.toFixed(4)}i&lt;br&gt;
        &lt;strong&gt;\u222e f(z)/(z\u2212z\u2080) dz = 2\u03c0i \u00b7 f(z\u2080) = ${resRe} + ${resIm}i&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;`;
    } else {
